Separatist - Closure [Metal] (2014) (mp3)

A solo project that used to be a full band but totally isn't anymore
Separatist are am experimental death metal band from Tasmania. They have been playing together in various forms for a few years now, but the current line-up has been playing since the start of 2006. With influences that range all the way from Tool to Psycroptic, Meshuggah to Dimmu Borgir, Separatist are a band thats not to be taken lightly... In 2008 we released our debut album, The Motionless Apocalypse, and it recieved worldwide acclaim from sources like Metal Hammer and Blunt magazines.
